If using local Solr + RecordManager installations, this directory includes
example files 'sample_data.xml' and 'sample_datasources.ini' to import a
small sample dataset in MARC format to the Solr index of the virtual
machine being installed and provisioned.

See '/usr/local/RecordManager/conf/datasources.ini.sample' inside the
virtual machine and RecordManager docs to create an actual institution
configuration for more proper use.

Adjust the RECMAN_SOURCE, RECMAN_DATASOURCE & RECMAN_DATA values in
ubuntu.conf/centos.conf files when using your own data.
